snippet.description:
Taken from Philly B's debut album "Let It Play", out in Digital stores 27th July 2015

ORDER NOW: https://phillydriven.bandcamp.com/

Philly Driven is kicking down the doors with this debut release featuring LDZ frontman & all-round vibalist, Dabbla.  'All riiise!!!' for King Lawrence Piffburn (Dabbla) & Sir Phillington Billit (Philly B.) as they embark on their mission into London town to greet the masses!

You Suck is the first of a series of singles we will be dropping in the lead up to Philly B's debut LP - "Let it Play".  

Check us out: 

http://phillydriven.com
http://dabbla.com

All rights reserved © Philly Driven 2013
For all usage please contact info@phillydriven.com
 
Vocals by Dabbla
Flute & Clarinet by Steve Gregory
Production by Philly B

Video by Philip Bennett
Assistant Director Lewis Lindgren
Additional Camera Work: Joe Joyce & Lewis Lindgren
Thanks to Omar Teknology & Jasmeet 'Dubtician' Singh
